HOW TO STOP YOUR PPC CAMPAIGNS FROM TURNING INTO A FIERY PIT OF MONEY DOOM

Stop Bad Targeting

Make more money from every campaign.

Why you'll fail without Ad Alchemy

You'll bid on straight up bad keywords

Over 50% of the keywords that people use are terrible. They are either informational or navigational and will never turn into a sale and waste your cash.

You'll miss great keywords that generate sales

There are so many keywords that you are currently not bidding on that you should be. You're effectively losing money by not targeting those people.

Why you'll win with Ad Alchemy

Filter your keywords to find the ones that convert

We analyze your keywords and allow you to filter them into commercial, transactional, informational and navigational. You can then just focus on using the ones that convert (hint: it's the first two).

Discover your competitors winning keywords

Use the competitor analysis (interrogate competitor and competitor comparison) reports to discover what keywords are working for your competitors that you are not using. Let them spend their budget finding the winning keywords.

Find new converting keywords

Brainstorm new keywords for your niche that you may not have thought of. Then filter by keyword intent to make sure you only use the ones that will actually convert.

Expand on the keywords that are already working

Got keywords that are already working? Expand on those keywords to go deeper and again, filter what is found by keyword intent to make sure you only use the ones that will convert.

Use AI Clustering to thematically group keywords

Got a huge list of keywords from other tools, but don't know how to sort them? Use our AI tool to thematically sort them into groups so you can create ads that match.

Create negative keyword sets

What you negative match is as important as what keywords you bid on. Use our negative keyword sets or create your own.

Ad Alchemy Targeting Features

Use the right keyword targeting from the very first click.

Keyword Intent Analysis

Filter by keyword intent so you can filter out the navigational and informational keywords and leave those that have the best chance of converting.

Suggest Keyword Tool

Need ideas for new keywords to target? We've got you fam. Plus we give lots of extra metrics like our sweet spot and keyword intent overlays.

Expand Keyword Tool

Got keywords that are already working? Let's expand those keywords to drive more volume! Plus filter by keyword intent to keep the converters.

AI Keyword Cluster Tool

Use our AI tool to take your big list of keywords and sort them into thematic clusters to base your new campaigns around with laser focus.

Competitor Analysis Tools

Don't guess what your competitors are doing. Just run a competitor interrogation or competitor comparison report and find out!

Keyword Tools

Slice, dice and clean up your keywords like a Ninja with the Ad Alchemy keyword tools.
